Mr Jiayong's mini kitchen was soon closed down by airport officials, but fellow travellers and stores within the terminal  helped him with food until he was able to fly home yesterday.

He had been forced to travel to Singapore for work to help look after his family and used the rice cooker for preparing meals during his month long employment.

